===Proper noun===
'''the East'''

# The [[eastern|Eastern]] [[world]]; the regions, primarily situated in the Eastern [[hemisphere|Hemisphere]], whose culture is derived from India or China.
#* '''1868:''' [[w:Wilkie Collins|Wilkie Collins]], ''The Moonstone''
#*:I remember a hearty welcome; a prodigious supper, which would have fed a whole village in the '''East'''
# The [[Eastern bloc]]; the eastern countries of [[Europe]].
# The eastern [[state]]s of the [[United States]].
# The [[eastern]] part of any region.

